                          Initial letters of the divine names or their abbreviations are rubricated.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus from="150va" to="150vb"/>
                           <desc type="Comment">Note on the symbolic meaning of the constituents of the temple. The note is very crudely written in Amharic. Different parts of the church and its utensils are identified with God, Mary, angels and saints. 
                              Below the note, there is a hardly legible ownership note.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="am">በስመ፡ ነጠል፡ ፪፡ እደ፡ ዕርቅ፡ ሙሴና፡ ኢያሱ፡ ሰረገላ፡ አሮን፡ ምሰሶው፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ መቅደስ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ መቃን፡ ዮሴፍና፡ ኒቆዲሞስ፡ መድረክ፡ መቃብሩ፡ ክርስቶስ…</q>
                        </item>
